{"tid":963481,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)本年最後一次殺狗","createTime":"2018-12-31T15:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T17:30:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a62dc704c147cfb66efb05d0534c920000209968","tid":963481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=58a6df20\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ce9992b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a3a28924\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.約翰&middot;維克是一位退隱江湖的殺手，不久前失去了因病而逝的妻子海倫，這令他哀傷不已，舉辦完葬禮後連過去同為殺手的馬克斯也前來關心他。不久後，約翰收到了一隻海倫生前為他訂的小狗黛西，海倫希望黛西能陪伴約翰，而他也將黛西視為朋友。一早，約翰開著他69年的福特野馬愛車和黛西出門，當到一間加油站加油時，塔拉索夫家族的領頭維果的兒子約謝夫想要和約翰買下他的車，但被約翰拒絕，約謝夫便此心生不滿。當晚，約謝夫和另外兩位朋友格雷戈里、維克多蒙面闖入約翰家中，不但襲擊了他還殺死了黛西，之後便搶了車庫裡的福特野馬後離開。約翰從昏迷中醒來後發現奄奄一息的黛西爬到了自己的身旁斷了氣，之後便將牠埋於後院<br />\n<br />\n2.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面..<br />\n<br />\n11 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bd77922c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6yZlErWEhdfD04ocpivlSv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0b4ee891\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1814dbf9775198dbc29201171f19e34d3e284cb6","tid":963481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50cef9cfa57e754748b0f26a083d4ce81f7fe0f","tid":963481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"新年快樂"},{"pid":"53c78207f26a6604d02a208312f0988ebc34e9c9","tid":963481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}